title: Replace Honeycomb 2x pool WBTC to new asset in Stage 7
body:
## Summary
For the first time, let's decide on an asset to be staked in Honeycomb Stage 7, which will commence right around 1st Jan 2021.

## Specification
Two new assets are nominated based on the discussion at Honey Finance Forum thread: https://forum.myhoney.finance/t/proposal-campaign-replace-honeycomb-2x-pool-wbtc-to-new-asset-in-stage-7/13

The winning ERC-20 token will then be announced and shall replace the current WBTC pool (2x Honey Rewards) in Stage 7 of Honeycomb.

## Options
1. TOMOE (https://etherscan.io/token/0x05d3606d5c81eb9b7b18530995ec9b29da05faba)
2. DAI (https://etherscan.io/token/0x6b175474e89094c44da98b954eedeac495271d0f)
3. WBTC (https://etherscan.io/token/0x2260fac5e5542a773aa44fbcfedf7c193bc2c599)
author: 0x179047339A1c38F8A7820D89B401fD32179158a0
